section_summary: The text appears to be a transcript of a session or meeting, possibly in a legislative body. The date mentioned is June 20, 2023, and the page number is 56. The text includes the opening statement by the session's chairperson, Mr. Marzouk Al-Habaini, and the second item on the agenda, which is the swearing-in of members according to Article 91 of the constitution. One member, Mr. Ahmed Lari, takes the oath and pledges loyalty to the country, the prince, and the constitution, as well as to defend the people's freedoms and interests. The text also mentions the General Secretariat of the Council of Parliament and the administration of the sessions.
